          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "During a bullfight, a drunk suddenly wandered into the middle of the ring.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 15.52,
      "endTime": 22.09
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The crowd began to shout, but the drunk was unaware of the danger.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 22.1,
      "endTime": 28.64
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The bull was busy with the matador at the time,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.65,
      "endTime": 33.02,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Busy",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "忙碌的"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but it suddenly caught sight of the drunk who was shouting rude remarks and waving a red cap.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.03,
      "endTime": 41.13,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Red",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "红色的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Apparently sensitive to criticism,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.14,
      "endTime": 44.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "the bull forgot all about the matador and charged at the drunk.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 44.66,
      "endTime": 50.68,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The crowd suddenly grew quiet.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 50.69,
      "endTime": 54.47
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The drunk, however, seemed quite sure of himself.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 54.48,
      "endTime": 59.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When the bull got close to him, he clumsily stepped aside to let it pass.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 59.38,
      "endTime": 66.5,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The crowd broke into cheers and the drunk bowed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.51,
      "endTime": 71.32
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "By this time, however three men had come into the ring and they quickly dragged the drunk to safety.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 71.33,
      "endTime": 80.1,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
